subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Justise Winslow had 16 points as the top-seeded Blue Devils advanced to the Final Four, where the senior Quinn Cook will have a chance to ease the sting of a 2013 loss.
